flowchart LR
  A[Case surfaced to Moderator Queue] --> B[Moderator Context Panel]
  B --> C[What Moderator Sees]
  C --> C1["Signal summary (not raw outputs)"]
  C --> C2["Confidence band + rationale"]
  C --> C3["Recent session timeline (LIVE)"]
  C --> C4["Relevant aggregates (history, audience shifts)"]

  B --> D{Moderator Decision}
  D -- Approve --> E["Apply recommended action<br/>prompt/friction/limit"]
  D -- Override --> F["Choose alternative action<br/>or lower severity"]
  D -- No Action --> G[Dismiss / monitor]

  E --> H[Audit Log]
  F --> H
  G --> H
  H --> I["Feedback Capture<br/>structured reason codes"]
  I --> J["Offline review loop<br/>policy + ops + product"]